  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Sales & Marketing Intern",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>a. Social Media & Content Support</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in creating content for FB, Instagram, TikTok, RED, and other platforms</li><li>Support photo/video shoots, BTS content, and simple editing (CapCut / Canva)</li><li>Help prepare captions, hashtags, and posting schedules</li><li>Ensure content aligns with brand tone and guidelines</li></ul><p><strong>b. Campaign & Activation Support</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in executing marketing campaigns, promotions, and collaborations</li><li>Support live events, pop-ups, and in-store activations when required</li><li>Help coordinate timelines, deliverables, and simple tracking sheets</li></ul><p><strong>c. Research & Idea Generation</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct basic market, trend, and competitor research</li><li>Monitor social media trends, viral formats, and content ideas</li><li>Propose content ideas and campaign concepts during team discussions</li></ul><p><strong>d. Data & Performance Tracking</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in tracking social media performance and campaign results</li><li>Compile weekly or monthly performance summaries</li><li>Help identify what content performs well and why</li></ul><p><strong>e. Administrative & Team Support</strong></p><ul><li>Maintain content folders, calendars, and simple reports</li><li>Support coordination with designers, videographers, or outlets</li><li>Assist the marketing team with ad-hoc tasks as needed</li></ul>",
